@@ -0,0 +1,11 @@
+FROM maven:3.6.0-jdk-11-slim AS build
+RUN mkdir -p /workspace
+WORKDIR /workspace
+COPY pom.xml /workspace
+COPY src /workspace/src
+RUN mvn -f pom.xml clean package
+
+FROM openjdk:11
+COPY --from=build /workspace/target/*.jar app.jar
+EXPOSE 8080
+ENTRYPOINT ["java","-jar","app.jar"]

diff --git a/docker-compose.yml b/docker-compose.yml
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..e75609b
--- /dev/null
+++ b/docker-compose.yml
@@ -0,0 +1,53 @@
+version: '3.7'
+services:
+  db:
+    image: postgres:12.3-alpine
+    container_name: postgres
+    ports:
+      - 5432:5432
+    restart: always
+    environment:
+      POSTGRES_DB: mentorship
+      POSTGRES_USER: postgres
+      POSTGRES_PASSWORD: password
+      PGDATA: /var/lib/postgresql/data/pgdata
+    volumes:
+      - pg-data:/var/lib/postgresql/data/pgdata
+    networks:
+      - backend
+
+  orb-server:
+    build:
+      context: mentorship-backend
+    container_name: orb-server
+    environment:
+      POSTGRES_HOST: db
+    ports:
+      - 8080:8080
+    depends_on:
+      - db
+    restart: always
+    networks:
+      - backend
+      - frontend
+
+  orb-client:
+    build:
+      context: mentorship-client
+      args:
+        REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL: http://127.0.0.1:8080
+    container_name: orb-client
+    ports:
+      - 3000:80
+    restart: always
+    depends_on:
+      - orb-server
+    networks:
+      - frontend
+
+volumes:
+  pg-data:
+
+networks:
+  backend:
+  frontend:
\ No newline at end of file

diff --git a/mentorship-client/Dockerfile b/mentorship-client/Dockerfile
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..eb0353a
--- /dev/null
+++ b/mentorship-client/Dockerfile
@@ -0,0 +1,23 @@
+# BUILD
+FROM node:14.4.0-alpine3.10 AS build
+WORKDIR /app
+
+COPY package.json yarn.lock ./
+RUN yarn install
+
+COPY . ./
+
+ARG REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL
+ENV REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL=${REACT_APP_API_BASE_URL}
+
+RUN yarn run build
+
+# RUN
+FROM nginx:1.19.0-alpine
+
+COPY --from=build /app/build /var/www
+COPY nginx.conf /etc/nginx/nginx.conf
+
+EXPOSE 80
+
+ENTRYPOINT ["nginx","-g","daemon off;"]
\ No newline at end of file
